A '''gatling gauntlet''' was a weapon usually worn by [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] and [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]]. It consisted of several barrels mounted on a wristband and had the ability to shoot a variety of ammunition types, from small metal projectiles to much larger spikes.

The gatling gauntlet was made popular by the bounty hunter [[Durge/Legends|Durge]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], and made a comeback with bounty hunters and mercenaries such as [[Bar-Kooda]] and [[Glott]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

{{Weapon-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
In the real world, the term "Gatling gun", referring to multi barreled automatic weapons, is named after [[Wikipedia:Richard J. Gatling|Richard Jordan Gatling]] and [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gatling_gun early machine gun] he invented. The may make the Gatling gauntlet an accidental [[Wikipedia:Earth|Earth]] reference.

